data.description: Location ! Location ! Location ! Experience coastal luxury living at its finest! This stunning ranch  is beautifully updated and located in sought after Point Pleasant. Only minutes from down town shopping, dining, entertainment, and the beaches.  Indulge your culinary senses in the modern kitchen with granite countertops, white cabinets,  top-of-the-line Viking stove and Sub-Zero refrigerator. Freshly painted bedrooms & den. Two full updated baths. Den with barn door could be a potential 3rd bedroom. Hardwood floors, vaulted ceiling, recessed lights, smart technology thermostat & home speaker. Modern sliding  glass doors leading to the backyard oasis. Step outside to a refinished deck, in-ground  saltwater pool with new cover, and newly installed vinyl fence. Too many amenities to list!
